YoDC
YoDC will be comprising of two programs (peer side and hub side). Peer will have nick name and some share files and folders. These files and folders are stored in the tree form. Peer will connect to hub and send this object to hub. Hub in return will send the information of all the online users. Peer can then browse file list of any online user and can download the file from their file list. Peer can also query for any file from hub and hub will reply with the file list allowing peer to download file or directory. There will also be the feature of common messaging peers can collectively.
